descriptionHtml:
This is a RaceMenu Preset I based on a League of Legends comic strip. She's Darius' dead girlfriend. Not much more to say.. she's pretty hot. 11/10 would bang... just download it >_>

Note: These presets use the Nord race (there is a sculpt .nif file in the optional files for those of you that wanna use other races).

[b][size=3]Requirements: [/size][/b]
[list=1]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Complexion[/url] for UNP with installer's optional add-ons (Eyes, Freckles, Brows, makeup, etc.) 
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?#content]The Eyes of Beauty[/url] (make sure this overwrites Fair Skin's eyes!)
[/list][size=3][b]Recommended:[/b] [/size]
[list=1]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/63920/?]Test HDT Earrings[/url]
[*][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28740/?]THEHAGs Private Tattoos for UNP[/url] - wood and imperial styles look nice. 
[*]My Bodyslide presets - "[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/85202/?]Dangerous Curves[/url]" and "[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/85223?]Scrumptious Curvature[/url]" - look quite nice with this character!
[/list][b][size=3]Installation:[/size][/b]
[list=1]
[*]Extract the file and get the jslot out. 
[*]Main Skyrim Folder > Data > SKSE > Plugins > chargen > Presets > Put the file in here!
[*]you can import the chargen stuff with racemenu sculpting tab (it displays the pathway I believe).
[/list]
author: wnisewond
